Nurses gathered online Tuesday night to honor those we've lost in the #COVID19 fight.

Listen to their names. 
Honor our fallen. 
Help us fight like hell for the living. 

Call (202) 335-6015 now. Demand the Senate do everything in its power to #ProtectNurses. https://t.co/afjJy3oXn6
